+ * Copyright (C) 2001 Greg Kroah-Hartman (greg@kroah.com)
+ *
+ * History:
+ *
+ * 2001-10-13 - 0.1 js
+ *   - first version
+ * 2001-11-03 - 0.2 js
+ *   - simplified buffering, one-shot URBs for writing
+ * 2001-11-10 - 0.3 js
